                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Loomis</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Caracas</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1899-10-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 20, 1899</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>President of Venezuela left for La Guaira daylight with 800 men. Did not resign
                    office. Some disorder here. Heavy bomb dynamite exploded against house Matos,
                    formerly minister finance.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Loomis.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
